{
  "stem": "2833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And something happened there, which had a great influence on my life in Terezin, because I met a-- I was asked to help out at the doctor's tent.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had a tent there, and if somebody was really ill, he had to examine them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they were sent home or not, depending on what he found.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was supposed to stand guard in front of the door to that tent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had a chair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one lady came with her very old mother, who didn't feel good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I gave her my chair and had her sit down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And later on, this same lady, the daughter, when we came to Terezin, helped me to get a position which made life a little easier for me from the beginning, because she wanted to kind of say thank you.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But anyway, after three days, we got on a train-- regular train-- and went to Bohusovice, because there was no railway going into Terezin yet.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we marched from there into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was a little town, which was originally built by Empress Maria Theresa, for the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's why the town has mostly army barracks-- huge, huge army barracks-- which had been closed for, I don't know, 50 or 60 years, or how long-- or even longer, probably.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And what they did first-- it was a Czech village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were only in army barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And every time a new transport came, they opened another barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They had women and men separate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And children, depending on the age, were either-- the little boys with their father, and little girls went with their mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And each army barrack had their own kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
